title: Doctor.Who.Planet.of.the.Dead.Special.2009.HQ.Edition.HDTV.x264-
description:
Doctor.Who.Planet.of.the.Dead.Special.2009.HQ.Edition.HDTV.x264-D734

MM couldn't do the HQ edition like normal, so i figured i would do one.
I don't know about other guys x264 in .mkv encodes for this ep but this was done from a HDTV source instead of the lower quality PDTV source that's normally used for the HQ encodes (about time they aired doctor who in HD). But don't worry about a logo as there is no bbc hd logo.
This is 550mb instead of 350mb because the episode is 59 minutes long as appose to the normal ~43 minutes.
If you want more quality then grab the 1.45gb 720p x264 or the 6.73gb 1080MBAFF h264 source.
